-neighbours">Good Neighbors</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/hana-vu">Hana Vu</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/molly-payton">Molly Payton</a> 、Emily Jeffri、Sienna Spiro 和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/jacob-alon">Jacob Alon</a> 。</p><p>他们加入了<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/all-points-east-2024-mitksi-announced-as-final-headliner-buy-tickets-3615254">之前宣布的特别嘉宾 Beabadoobee、TV Girl、Ethel Cain、Arlo Parks、Sir Chloe、Wasia Project、Infinity Song、Wisp、Towa Bird、Strawberry Guy 和 bby 的行列</a>。米茨基的精彩表演将标志着她在为期 10 天的伦敦音乐节上的首次亮相。</p><p>节日日期定于 8 月 18 日星期日在伦敦维多利亚公园举行。 <a href="https://www.ticketmaster.co.uk/all-points-east-tickets/artist/5245909?irgwc=1&amp;utm_source=2862475-NME%20Networks%20Media%20Limited&amp;utm_medium=affiliate&amp;utm_campaign=2862475&amp;awtrc=&amp;clickId=RNAxOYVh5xyPWWl31GWJ3xHTUkH3XD09nRXHRo0&amp;camefrom=CFC_BUYAT_2862475&amp;ircid=7559" target="_blank" rel="noopener">请访问此处</a>购买门票。 </p><figure id="attachment_3760218" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3760218" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3760218" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/All-Points-East-2024-Mitski-poster.-Credit-PRESS.jpg" alt="All Points East 2024 Mitski 海报。图片来源：新闻界" width="2000" height="2000" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/All-Points-East-2024-Mitski-poster.-Credit-PRESS.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/All-Points-East-2024-Mitski-poster.-Credit-PRESS-150x150.jpg 150w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/All-Points-East-2024-Mitski-poster.-Credit-PRESS-400x400.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/All-Points-East-2024-Mitski-poster.-Credit-PRESS-800x800.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/All-Points-East-2024-Mitski-poster.-Credit-PRESS-696x696.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/All-Points-East-2024-Mitski-poster.-Credit-PRESS-1392x1392